No. D-2477. In the Matter of Brian Grayson West. 561 U.S. 1049, 131 S. Ct. 51,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1141,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5681. August 16, 2010.

Brian Grayson West, of Brooklandville, Maryland, having requested to resign as a member of the Bar of this Court, it is ordered that his name be stricken from the roll of attorneys permitted to the practice of law before this Court. The Rule to Show Cause, issued on July 26, 2010, is discharged.
